name: #1 - Law of Intention
description:
The Laws of Manifestation

#1 - Law of Intention
There's more to it than just thinking a thought - as thoughts alone are meaningless.

The majority of our thoughts aren't even true - but we're having the same thoughts over and over again, and if you think something enough - you'll start to believe it.

So observe your thoughts. Set your intentions. And remember not to worry about the specifics.
